data.description: Gorgeous...with bells and whistles! Newer roof, newer front door with transom window. Brazilian Walnut HW floors. Custom shelves with LED on FP Wall. LED landscape lights. All LED lights throughout house. Upgraded to 96% variable speed furnace and 3T AC unit. Custom master bath with walk-in tile shower and mahogany cabinets, granite counters and heated tile floor. Theratre area is basement with built-in speakers.  32'x24' attached ICF building with radiant heated floor could be garage, in-law suite, entertainment area, etc. Back yard covered patio with electric and BBQ island has water fall feature; hot tub with gazebo.
